thread.title_full: Extra Space Storage reviewed by Paul West

author: Paul West
title: Paul West
text: Better than expected. The "first month free" is no bull. It really was free with no commitment. The people at my site are fantastic. There were no hidden fees and is maintained awesome especially after the snow. I opted to take their insurance because it's very inexpensive and no deductible. I would totally recommend it
